00:39:31,932 --> 00:39:34,932
(Noriko) That's... for someone like me.

506
00:39:37,932 --> 00:39:39,932
I like it. (Noriko) Huh?

507
00:39:39,932 --> 00:39:43,932
An adult woman working hard.

508
00:39:43,932 --> 00:39:46,932
I understand. Living desperately...

509
00:39:46,932 --> 00:39:50,932
《Please try to live as hard as you can》

510
00:39:50,932 --> 00:39:55,932
(Noriko) Huh? Mr. Suzuki?

511
00:39:55,932 --> 00:40:00,932
(Sumiharu) 《Why do you talk about that woman...》

512
00:40:00,932 --> 00:40:15,932
♬～

513
00:40:18,932 --> 00:40:20,932
(Aoi) I guess it's no good after all. (Sound of placing a vase)

514
00:40:20,932 --> 00:40:23,932
(Okuda) Eh, what are you doing? (Aoi) Wow. Have you come again?

515
00:40:23,932 --> 00:40:26,932
No, you smell like flowers right now... you're an idol, after all.

516
00:40:26,932 --> 00:40:28,932
It's noisy. (Okuda) Huh? What happened? What happened?

517
00:40:28,932 --> 00:40:31,932
What are you imitating? (Aoi) It smelled.

518
00:40:31,932 --> 00:40:35,932
Huh? (Aoi) Just for a moment the other day.

519
00:40:35,932 --> 00:40:38,932
(Okuda) Does that mean you're probably getting better?

520
00:40:38,932 --> 00:40:43,932
No, I don't know. There's no way to be sure.

521
00:40:43,932 --> 00:40:47,932
No, is there something I can get away with without knowing?

522
00:40:47,932 --> 00:40:49,932
Huh? (Okuda) Something➡

523
00:40:49,932 --> 00:40:51,932
I don't know what the circumstances are ➡

524
00:40:51,932 --> 00:40:53,932
How important is the scent of flowers to you?

525
00:40:53,932 --> 00:40:56,932
I know. ➡

526
00:40:56,932 --> 00:40:58,932
Is that so?

527
00:40:58,932 --> 00:41:01,932
If there's even the slightest chance, hang on.

528
00:41:03,932 --> 00:41:23,932
♬～

529
00:41:23,932 --> 00:41:43,932
♬～

530
00:41:43,932 --> 00:41:46,932
♬～

531
00:41:46,932 --> 00:41:50,932
(Aoi) 《I like that picture》

532
00:41:50,932 --> 00:41:53,932
《Lively➡

533
00:41:53,932 --> 00:41:56,932
I can almost smell it➡

534
00:41:56,932 --> 00:42:00,932
Because it reminds me of happy feelings》

535
00:42:04,932 --> 00:42:06,932
(Aoi) 《No matter how hard it is》

536
00:42:06,932 --> 00:42:26,932
♬～

