547
00:44:29,932 --> 00:44:32,932
Long time no see, Sumiharu-kun.

548
00:44:36,932 --> 00:44:38,932
Hehe...

549
00:44:38,932 --> 00:44:41,932
Hehe.

550
00:44:41,932 --> 00:44:43,932
